00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:47,330
If one day we can really move
to China Hong Kong,

284
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:48,620
that would be amazing.

285
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,490
It's pretty close to Shunde.

286
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,900
My whole family lives there.

287
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:53,630
We wouldn't have to worry
about anything.

288
00:25:55,590 --> 00:25:56,530
People always say

289
00:25:56,960 --> 00:26:00,380
China Hong Kong is warm all year round.

290
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:03,050
Your leg will get much better
over there.

291
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,980
There's a place called Queen's Road.

292
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:10,490
They say all the fancy stuff
is on Queen's Road.

293
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:13,380
Rich folks live in Mid-Levels.

294
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,490
In the Mid-Levels area,

295
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,980
if you open the window,

296
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,220
you can see Victoria Harbour
right there.

297
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:22,550
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

298
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:37,700
When we're settled,

299
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,700
maybe we could have a kid.

300
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:47,250
Before, we kept saying, let's wait.

301
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:50,090
We wanted to give our child
a better life.

302
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,520
I've finally understood something.

303
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:56,940
As long as we're both safe and sound,

304
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:58,980
that's the best life we could ask for.

305
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:00,700
Don't you agree?

306
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:15,700
Yin,

307
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,980
you've been through so much
all these years.

308
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,250
Good times are just around the corner.

309
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,220
Very soon.

310
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,460
Liang,

311
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:18,140
we've spent half our lives
scheming against others.

312
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,770
This time,

313
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:26,290
you even included me in your schemes.

314
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:32,770
You little wretch!

315
00:28:41,510 --> 00:28:42,250
Liang,

316
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:49,490
people make their small plans,

317
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:52,730
but Heaven

318
00:28:54,350 --> 00:28:56,700
has the ultimate plan.

319
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:01,980
Let it...

320
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,670
They say a real man must be ruthless.

321
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:56,980
Mr. Liang,

322
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,530
you really have guts.

323
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:08,980
So what kind of explanation do you need?

324
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:22,730
Back then in Japan, the one
who helped you rise up

325
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,700
is

326
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,980
Mrs. Liang.

327
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:40,140
Ye Yin sheltered
under the Japanese invaders,

328
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,280
and betrayed the central command.

329
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,190
Despite repeated efforts

330
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,980
to dissuade her,

331
00:30:54,650 --> 00:30:56,790
she launched a surprise attack
on the Shanghai Bureau.

332
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:06,980
Dozens of our comrades died
in the flames.

333
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,050
This crime is beyond forgiveness.

334
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:21,050
Would this explanation satisfy you?

335
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:30,730
You seized the stronghold
in the Japanese Concession

336
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:34,420
and avenged our brothers in Shanghai.

337
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:40,460
Plus the gold from the warehouse
in China Hong Kong.

338
00:31:43,170 --> 00:31:44,440
That's three major achievements.

339
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:47,940
Mr. Liang,

340
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:52,250
