341
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:55,180
Thank you, Chief Cao.

342
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,460
May I take my wife's body back
to Chongqing?

343
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,940
Sure, let's go.

344
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,420
I didn't expect

345
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:45,180
so many things to happen in one night.

346
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:50,940
Sorry I didn't help you.

347
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,420
But I was about to look for you too.

348
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:58,900
Now Sasaki is dead,

349
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:00,720
and Liang Jingyuan has gone missing.

350
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:03,530
The Sword Thrust Operation

351
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:05,530
will be the sole intel channel

352
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:06,770
within the New Government.

353
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:09,140
What a pity.

354
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,330
We can't share it.

355
00:33:16,550 --> 00:33:17,700
That's quite a bold move.

356
00:33:21,050 --> 00:33:22,690
Are you in such a hurry
to drive me away?

357
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,580
Luo Han's about to board the ship
back to Chongqing.

358
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,940
Once he reports

359
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:33,280
your and Xian Biyun's identities

360
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:34,530
to my superiors,

361
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:37,730
Chongqing will spare no effort

362
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,940
to take both your lives.

363
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,620
And these are

364
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,460
ship tickets to China Hong Kong.

365
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:47,860
Now Grand Duke Tonoji is dead.

366
00:33:49,010 --> 00:33:50,560
I've joined the Pacification Committee.

367
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,530
I no longer need Joseph Lee.

368
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,730
To the public, I will say

369
00:33:56,030 --> 00:33:58,460
that Joseph Lee can no longer
continue working

370
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,940
due to the worsening of his tumor.

371
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:02,080
Once you get to China Hong Kong,

372
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:04,280
decide for yourself where to go next.

373
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:08,260
Do you think

374
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:09,960
that after all this,

375
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:12,690
death can still threaten me?

376
00:34:20,450 --> 00:34:20,880
By the way,

377
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,210
about your mother,

378
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:25,090
I'm sorry.

379
00:34:28,300 --> 00:34:28,820
Tastes great.

380
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,690
Did you make this sauce?

381
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:35,980
Your mother made this.

382
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:38,460
This is from Baimahu.

383
00:34:42,110 --> 00:34:44,050
Actually, I made that sauce myself.

384
00:34:45,190 --> 00:34:47,130
Your mother is safe in Baimahu.

385
00:34:47,150 --> 00:34:49,300
My people are just
protecting her discreetly.

386
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,150
They haven't disturbed her at all.

387
00:34:51,700 --> 00:34:52,980
When you get to China Hong Kong,

388
00:34:53,410 --> 00:34:54,750
I'll make sure she gets there too.

389
00:34:55,550 --> 00:34:56,210
Really?

390
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:01,340
Do you think threatening me

391
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:02,900
using my mother repeatedly

392
00:35:03,590 --> 00:35:04,740
will still work on me?

393
00:35:06,450 --> 00:35:07,950
Do you think I'd leave her in Baimahu?

394
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:13,860
You're right.

395
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,530
I forgot

396
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:16,270
you're an organized person now,
aren't you?

397
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:19,460
Alright then.

398
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:24,650
From now on, let's stay out
of each other's way.

399
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:26,820
You work at the Cryptography Institute,

400
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:28,770
and I work
at the Pacification Committee.

401
00:35:30,110 --> 00:35:32,820
Let's not interfere with each other.

402
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:40,820
The noodles are here.

403
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,780
Noodles for you two.

404
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:04,460
Tastes great. Great!

405
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:06,900
Tastes just like two years ago.

406
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:07,900
Hasn't changed a bit.

407
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,050
Go on, try it.

408
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:21,780
This is really interesting.

409
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:24,940
I remember two years ago,

410
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:26,780
the two of us

411
00:36:28,030 --> 00:36:29,210
sat in this very spot.

412
00:36:31,070 --> 00:36:33,610
Back then you told me to stay.

413
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:36,740
But today you're pushing me to leave.

414
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,530
But back then,

415
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,090
you were full of fire,

416
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:46,570
more spirited than now.

417
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:48,740
Yeah.

418
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,570
We still fought side by side then.

419
00:36:57,070 --> 00:36:58,170
And that day,

420
00:36:59,190 --> 00:37:02,010
I actually felt guilty towards you.

421
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:08,420
You told me
you had three great strengths.

422
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,530
Sharp eye, good at imitation
and a great memory.

423
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,520
Turns out you weren't lying.

424
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:19,460
Eat some more.

425
00:37:20,550 --> 00:37:22,460
It's a long way back to Chongqing.

426
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:35,460
Sir, the soup's way too salty.

427
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:45,980
General Yasui asked me

428
00:37:46,180 --> 00:37:48,090
what exactly was going on
with the report letter

429
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:49,050
you wrote earlier.

430
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,460
Sorry, I told him the truth.

431
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,170
You colluded with Liang Jingyuan

432
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:55,630
and tried to set me up on purpose.

433
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,530
Those four people you see now

434
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,980
are all under General Yasui.

435
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:03,940
They're about to take you back
for questioning.

436
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,130
Aren't you afraid I might disclose

437
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:17,300
both your identity and that
of Xian Biyun to him?

438
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,980
I met Charlie back in the UK.

439
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:24,130
He insisted on becoming my assistant.

440
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:25,980
And I have no idea

441
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,420
who he is

442
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:28,820
or what he has done.

443
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:35,610
Do you think General Yasui

444
00:38:36,590 --> 00:38:37,650
would believe Charlie

445
00:38:38,630 --> 00:38:39,490
or would believe

446
00:38:39,510 --> 00:38:41,740
the only survivor of the Tonoji family,

447
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,210
Joseph Lee?

448
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,490
Don't forget

449
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:48,260
I'm the one who made you Joseph Lee.

450
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:01,900
Secretary Gu, please come with us.

451
00:39:08,610 --> 00:39:09,960
It's just an investigation, right?

452
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:10,690
No problem.

453
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,690
I will conduct it thoroughly.

454
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:17,380
Let's go.

455
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:18,980
Hold on a second.

456
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,530
Charlie,

457
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,490
tell them everything.

458
00:39:54,110 --> 00:39:55,460
Are you out of your mind?

459
00:39:57,190 --> 00:39:58,420
You were right just now.

460
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,490
It's just an investigation.

461
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:00,460
Not scary at all.

462
00:40:01,170 --> 00:40:02,340
But things are different now.

463
00:40:03,030 --> 00:40:04,660
You killed four Japanese
Military Police

464
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:06,090
